*** This repo will consist of my personal cybersecurity portfolio.

*** I have chosen to use the VMware Workstation Player for my virtual machine.


These are to be downloaded and installed onto the host machine.

Step One to Creating Your Home Lab
- Download your preferred Hypervisor.
-- https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads

Step Two:
- Download your Operating System(s).
------ Choose your Operating System based on your task (Offensive / Blue Team).
-- https://ubuntu.com/download/server      -- https://www.kali.org/get-kali/#kali-installer-images


*** Operating Systems like Kali are meant for Offensive Operations, while Ubuntu or Debian are meant for Blue Team Operations.

